                <mxCell id="p6" value="&lt;b&gt;OTA Update Manager&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr&gt;Over-the-Air fleet management.&lt;br&gt;Pushes new model versions to&lt;br&gt;vehicles. Supports canary and&lt;br&gt;staged rollout strategies.&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;AWS IoT / Azure IoT Hub&lt;/i&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EF6C00;fontColor=#fff;strokeColor=none;align=center;spacing=6;fontSize=12;" parent="1" vertex="1">
